<figureCitation id="5AC9447023205C329CBB60A6EC00A9D3" captionStart="Figure 1" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figure 1. Metachelifer cheni sp. nov., holotype male (A-J) and paratype female (K) A carapace B left chelicera C right leg I, lateral view D right leg IV, lateral view E coxa IV, ventral view F palp (minus chela) G chela, retrolateral view H chela, dorsal view I male genital area J male genitalia, dorsal view K female genital area. Scale bars: 0.50 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1103.78808.figure1" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/691634" pageId="0" pageNumber="171">1C</figureCitation>
