(Fig. 
<figureCitation id="8D452FBAB549D691B3B9ABFF4B80CB29" captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. A, B Metachelifer cheni sp. nov., dorsal views A holotype male B paratype female C, D M. mahnerti sp. nov., dorsal views C holotype male D paratype female. Scale bar: 1.00 mm (A-D)." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1103.78808.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/691638" pageId="0" pageNumber="171">5B</figureCitation>
